🎯 Revision Hook
When revising:

“0/1 Knapsack” → DP with backward loop.

Formula: dp[w] = max(dp[w], dp[w - weight] + value).

Backward loop ensures item used once.

👉 Memory trick:
“Knapsack: include or exclude, DP builds max value.”
